{"tid":2234063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吉爾吉斯總理及議長辭職　總統暗示願意下台","createTime":"2020-10-07T14:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T14:44:29.000Z","uid":64603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"93775407b9d8e5a2630b31655c74cd33bd7dad74","tid":2234063,"uid":64603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T14:44:29.000Z","msg":"中亞國家吉爾吉斯爆發不滿選舉結果的大規模示威，示威者闖入總統府及國會大樓，與警方爆發衝突，造成至少1死、6百多人受傷，總理博羅諾夫和議長茹馬別科夫宣布辭職。<br />\n<br />\n總統熱恩別科夫表示，準備把責任轉交給強勢領袖，暗示願意下台，但未有透露更多詳情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTMAHKg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTMAHKg.jpg&h=761692c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553527-20201007.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553527-20201007.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5MorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=943872f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553527-20201007.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7ce500eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553527-20201007.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}